'''HD 20782'''是一個視星等7等的[[黃矮星|黃矮星]]，距離地球117光年，位於[[天爐座|天爐座]]。

==概要==
HD 20782和另一個恆星[[HD_20781|HD 20781]]組成[[聯星|聯星]]系統，而這兩顆恆星各有行星環繞。成員星中的伴星HD 20781和HD 20782之間的[[角距離|角距離]]高達252角秒，相當於9080天文單位<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aanda.org/index.php?option=com_article&access=bibcode&Itemid=129&bibcode=2007A%2526A...462..345DFUL |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2021-02-06 |archive-date=2019-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120093655/https://www.aanda.org/index.php?option=com_article&access=bibcode&Itemid=129&bibcode=2007A%2526A...462..345DFUL |dead-url=no }}</ref>。HD 20782的年齡大約是71 ± 4億年，質量接近太陽。2006年在主星HD 20782旁宣布發現[[系外行星|系外行星]] <ref name="Jones"/><ref>{{cite news|title=Notes for HD 20782 |cite web|url=http://exoplanet.eu/star.php?st=HD+20782|author=Schneider, J|work=The Extrasolar Planets Encyclopaedia|accessdate=2021-02-06|archive-date=2012-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120505094745/http://exoplanet.eu/star.php?st=HD+20782|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年在伴星[[HD_20781|HD 20781]]旁發現兩顆低質量的系外行星<ref>{{cite news|title=Notes for star HD 20781 |cite web|url=http://exoplanet.eu/star.php?st=HD+20781|author=Schneider, J|work=The Extrasolar Planets Encyclopaedia|accessdate=2011-09-12|archive-date=2013-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130314215628/http://exoplanet.eu/catalog/?f=%27HD%2020781%27+in+name|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite arXiv|eprint=1109.2497|class=astro-ph|title=The HARPS search for southern extra-solar planets XXXIV. Occurrence, mass distribution and orbital properties of super-Earths and Neptune-mass planets|author=Mayor, M. Marmier,M.  Lovis,C.  Udry,S.  Ségransan,D.  Pepe,F.  Benz,W.  Bertaux,J.-L.  Bouchy,F. Dumusque, G.  Curto,Lo  Mordasini,C. Queloz,D.  Santos,N. C. ''et al.''|year=2011}}</ref>。

